name: #002 / Neon Jellyfish
description:
FUTURE NEON SERIES

Fish are rarely found in the city harbour due to high levels of waste. Instead, neon jellyfish roam the waters, getting their unique fluorescent glow from absorbing toxic particles. Neon jellyfish signs warn citizens to avoid the water, but instead attract curious sightseers who gather to watch their ethereal display.

1080x1080 / 30fps
